    "Thus, we adopt the following DPOmixed (DPO-x) objective:",
    "where L SF T is the same objective optimized during the SFT training, and λ is the SFT loss coefficient.",
    "To generate real-user-driven dialogues that simulate user-system interactions, in a dual goal setting, we adopt a generation pipeline that leverages realworld conversational data (Gottardi et al., 2022) through data augmentation techniques.",
    "The resulting dialogues go beyond the scope of Choi et al. (2022) by adding contextual requests and requests not related to the task, thus better replicating real user behavior (Gottardi et al., 2022).",
